<Body>
	<Title>哈尔滨40名小学生疑似食物中毒入院治疗</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008年10月9日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Participant sid="s">新华网</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">10月9日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">信息</Denoter></Event></Sentence>：<Sentence><Event eid="e2">哈尔滨市平房区平新镇新华小学<Participant sid="s2">40名小学生</Participant><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">8日</Time>在<Location lid="2l">食堂</Location><Denoter did="d2" type="action">吃</Denoter>完<Object oid="o2">午饭</Object>后</Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>呕吐、头晕等<Object oid="o3">食物中毒症状</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e4">被紧急<Denoter did="d4" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l4">医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e5"><Denoter did="d5" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e6"><Time tid="t6" type="timeInterval">截至9日中午</Time>，仍有<Participant sid="s6">18名小学生</Participant>继续<Denoter did="d6" type="operation">住院</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e7">接受<Denoter did="d7" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>据了解，<Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">这些学生</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="action">发病</Denoter></Event>前<Event eid="e9"><Denoter did="d9" type="action">食用</Denoter>过<Object oid="o9">豆角</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
     
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">9日上午</Time>，<Participant sid="s10">记者</Participant>在<Location lid="l10">哈尔滨二四二医院儿科病房</Location><Denoter did="d10" type="perception">看到</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Location lid="l11">三四间病房内</Location><Denoter did="d11" type="action">住着</Denoter>正在治疗的<Participant sid="s11">小学生</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s12">有的</Participant>正在<Denoter did="d12" type="action">打点滴</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>据了解，孩子们来自平房区平新镇新华小学，年龄7岁到10岁。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e13">据哈尔滨二四二医院儿科主任<Participant sid="s13">陈松柏</Participant><Denoter did="d13" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e14"><Time tid="t14" type="timeInterval">8日下午4点半到晚7点半</Time>，<Participant sid="s14">该医院</Participant>陆续<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">接治</Denoter>了40名临床表现为恶心、呕吐、头晕的<Participant  oid="o14">小学生</Participant></Event>。由于学生人数较多情况紧急，<Event eid="e15"><Participant sid="s15">医院</Participant><Denoter did="d15" type="operation">开通</Denoter>了<Object oid="o15">绿色通道</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">当班医护人员</Participant>全部投入<Denoter did="d16" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17">卫生防疫部门</Participant>也到<Location lid="l17">现场</Location><Denoter did="d17" type="operation">取样</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e18"><Object oid="o18">发病原因</Object>正在<Denoter did="d18" type="operation">调查</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">陈松柏</Participant><Denoter did="d19" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，这些小学生具有较典型的食物中毒症状，诊断结果为由饮食不当引起的胃肠功能紊乱。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e20"><Participant sid="s20">医院</Participant>对<Participant oid="o20">其</Participant>采取了洗胃、催吐、输液等<Denoter did="d20" type="operation">治疗</Denoter>措施</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e21"><Time tid="t21" type="timeInterval">截至9日中午</Time>，有<Participant sid="s21">22名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d21" type="operation">出院</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e22">仍有<Participant sid="s22">18名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d22" type="operation">留院治疗</Denoter></Event>，目前情况基本稳定。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
